content:
Sure, below is a sample HTML page that outlines the advantages of a 4-day work week. I've included some basic styling for visual appeal and an image to illustrate the concept of work-life balance.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Advantages of a 4-Day Work Week</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-align: center;
        }
        ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 0;
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        li {
            background: #e8e8e8;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .image-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Advantages of a 4-Day Work Week</h1>
    <div class="image-container">
        <img src="https://example.com/work-life-balance.jpg" alt="Work-Life Balance">
    </div>
    <ul>
        <li>Increased productivity: Employees often accomplish more in less time due to improved focus and motivation.</li>
        <li>Improved work-life balance: More personal time allows employees to recharge, reducing burnout and stress.</li>
        <li>Enhanced employee satisfaction: A shorter work week can lead to higher job satisfaction and better retention rates.</li>
        <li>Environmental benefits: Fewer commuting days reduce carbon emissions and lower energy consumption.</li>
        <li>Cost savings: Reduced office utility costs and potential savings on salaries for hourly employees.</li>
    </ul>
</body>
</html>
```

Please note that you'll need to replace the image source URL (`https://example.com/work-life-balance.jpg`) with a valid image URL that you have access to or use a local image path. This example demonstrates a simple, clean layout using basic HTML and CSS to convey the advantages of a 4-day work week.
